data.description:
Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom house located on a corner lot! If you're searching for a cozy home, look no further. This property is perfect for first-time buyers, small families, or anyone looking to downsize without compromising comfort & style. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of the hardwood floors that flow throughout the main living areas. The natural light streaming in through the windows creates a bright & inviting atmosphere, making you feel right at home. The living room is a fantastic size for your gatherings & has a gas fireplace to keep you warm in the colder months. The bathroom has been beautifully tiled, adding a touch of elegance to your daily routine. It's the perfect space to relax & unwind after a long day. Plus, with two bedrooms, there's plenty of room for everyone to have their own tranquil retreat. But wait, there's more! This property also boasts a bonus room downstairs that can be transformed into your dream space. Whether you envision a home office, a playroom for the little ones, or a hobby room where you can unleash your creativity, the possibilities are endless. Located just minutes away from shops, restaurants, and entertainment options, this house offers both convenience and tranquility. Outside you will find a large yard, and spacious back deck for cooking and entertainment. The back lot is fenced in, & has a large storage building already for your convenience. There is ample parking beside the home ensures that you'll never have trouble finding a spot for your vehicles. Near the parking area is a garage that could easily be transformed to a workshop, or outside storage area. This home also features a plug in feature installed for an all home generator. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity. With its charm and location, this property won't stay on the market for long. Schedule your viewing today!
ALL INFORMATION GATHERED FROM 3RD PARTY & DEEMED RELIABLE. BUYER/BUYERS AGENT TO VERIFY
